{"tid":1269290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反送中】會展提早封場腰斬寵物展　參展商血本無歸誓追究損失︰多謝林鄭","createTime":"2019-06-30T13:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T14:39:32.000Z","uid":212626,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1e8fd3030a30937444399bad6e1982134de4b7b6","tid":1269290,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"政治也跟毛小孩有關。本港一年舉行兩個大型寵物節，每次都吸引許多寵物主人前往。今年原定於6月28至30日一連三日舉行的「優質寵物用品展2019」，昨日（29日）大會宣布，因政府基於安全及保安理由，今天（30日）的展覽將會取消，惹起很多寵物主人及參展商不滿。<br />\n<br />\n據大會Facebook專頁「優質寵物用品展」的帖文表示，寵物展已提前於6月29日（星期六）晚上9時結束，原訂於6月30日（星期日）於會場舉辦的展覽及各項活動亦將取消。作為主辦機構的展覽集團，對有關決定感到非常無奈。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有參展商得知消息後，於展場攤位貼上「多謝林鄭，最後1天」標語，以示不滿。有商戶亦留言表示，會追究一切損失。</span><br />\n<br />\n參展商「鈴蘭堂V&amp;A」更表明，會從法律途徑追究損失，明白政府為慶祝七一回歸，擔心保安問題而將會展封場，「但我哋作為苦主，都要為自己爭取！」<br />\n<br />\n另有參展商「Biopet -HK 寵然有限公司」在其Facebook專頁斥責政府，<span style=\"color: red;\">話封場就封場，好大個官威，不理會市民感受，「時間心血完全冇晒」</span>。而且現時會展外的路面也封閉，展商難以撤場，7月2日還要返回收拾殘局。<br />\n<br />\n參展商明言，雖然輸了寵物展、時間和心血，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不能輸掉香港，呼籲市民要團結撐住香港，「彩虹一定會出來，香港人加油！」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原定今日前往寵物展的寵物主人紛紛留言大罵政府做法，懷疑是「警察想包場入會展」、「入面好多糧同玩具啱佢地用」，有人更聽聞「3樓全部都係警察」，一定要參加七一遊行表達意見。<br />\nSource：經濟日報<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2388658/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2388658%2F&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=62124c4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2388658/</a>"},{"pid":"51564423dcd788e15de354c2aca005020e706d84","tid":1269290,"uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:53:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fsvyHss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfsvyHss.jpg&h=0e1b0658&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef1b1b7588dbd8cf456ec2029990ae0111fd1af7","tid":1269290,"uid":212626,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:55:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多謝林奠</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Do29fOd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDo29fOd.png&h=7bf300e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57f7ddeab9e8a2f73401c7ff9c29e0b4923998b7","tid":1269290,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6be44ecc96eeda7c09397973f2e55751a9ef38","tid":1269290,"uid":135,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:09:35.000Z","msg":"好似話大會定性左係因為天災所以取消<br />\n保險都冇得claim"},{"pid":"e684b4149b4ac0b8e60fbe5cb73b8ce167663f94","tid":1269290,"uid":35014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:09:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e39d633d9379e77230f58c65927459c2c5e80e50","tid":1269290,"uid":94834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:12:04.000Z","msg":"參展商聽日一齊發下夢"},{"pid":"bf6f6effa977dc26b479cff5dba429e01b16e3a7","tid":1269290,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e6be44ecc96eeda7c09397973f2e55751a9ef38","tid":1269290,"uid":135,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:09:35.000Z","msg":"好似話大會定性左係因為天災所以取消<br />\n保險都冇得claim"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:14:31.000Z","msg":"我都有睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能會有其他參展商行法律途徑"},{"pid":"435cf63b16b4ed9ea26f4c6d4feea7e47c468202","tid":1269290,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2oBz4Qu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2oBz4Qu.gif&h=7f037179&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac2fda748f12af4469f477ca1102947d4aaa542d","tid":1269290,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef1b1b7588dbd8cf456